{"tid":314284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港女響應世界無胸罩日","createTime":"2017-07-09T05:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T13:07:49.000Z","uid":72009,"like":5,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0112e995efff459eeda01fe1c4b323bc8fec99bf","tid":314284,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:13:42.000Z","msg":"港星歐陽巧瑩因2013年參加香港小姐選美而入行，不時在IG分享34C美胸辣照。她上個月露出大半個「西半球」，標註#freethenipple，推廣解放乳頭運動，今又響應「世界無胸罩日」（No Bra Day），換露東半球：「我希望香港人可以多了解這件事！解開胸前的束縛，防治乳癌！」<br />\n<br />\n歐陽巧瑩也引述醫學研究報導，「長時間穿著胸罩，會使鋼圈壓迫到胸部淋巴，淋巴液流動受阻可能使有害毒素留在乳房。特別是每天若穿戴胸罩超過12個小時以上，罹患乳癌機率比短時間穿戴或不穿者高出20倍，而且睡覺時穿著有鋼圈的胸罩也會降低睡眠品質」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170709/640_b0c5675a849f0a8c958619f31f483638.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170709%2F640_b0c5675a849f0a8c958619f31f483638.jpg&h=5c954a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170709/640_65a019727e7de5b5db21b29ad4c2d513.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170709%2F640_65a019727e7de5b5db21b29ad4c2d513.jpg&h=6a0c9603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港女，不奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e023b2e88755cab5bf115c442deb94717e46495a","tid":314284,"uid":74911,"like":1,"dislike":37,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:15:00.000Z","msg":"洗洗睡吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d771df319b327420ae521e8976c0d094e24cf9","tid":314284,"uid":25858,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:16:46.000Z","msg":"我地冇波架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a653133109fa70222c3098c6f01385f9bf92bed","tid":314284,"uid":7458,"like"